description: This is a strong area. The job description mentions C# and .NET as primary development languages. While this CV doesn't list C#, the mention of C++, Python, JavaScript, and TypeScript demonstrates programming versatility and a willingness to learn new languages, which is valuable since the description notes that the ideal candidate is a 'fast learner'.

This is a strong area. While the job description doesn't explicitly mention these frameworks, Reactjs is a popular frontend framework, and experience with it shows relevant skills for developing user interfaces, which are integral part of software development. Furthermore, the CV should be improved by mentioning a link to the GitHub or other portfolio with demonstrating code quality and projects.

This is a strong area. The 'Web Specialist' role within the Google Developer Group indicates involvement in tech sharing and community engagement, which aligns well with the desired traits of a 'people-oriented, friendly' candidate. This suggests good communication and collaborative skills. The candidate should have details of contributions and achievements, which might be a plus point.

This is a weak area. The job description prioritizes experience in public safety or public health. This project, while demonstrating technical skills, is not directly related to those fields. To improve, the candidate could seek out projects or volunteer opportunities in these areas to gain relevant experience.

This is a weak area. All the projects list the role as 'Frontend Developer'. The job description is for a Software Engineer I which requires the candidate to participate in all facets of software and system development life-cycle. To improve, the candidate can enhance their skill sets by focusing on backend developement.

This area is a weak area. While prizes and awards are good to have, the "City-ranking Excellence Contest 2023" isn't clearly related to software engineering. To make this section more relevant, the candidate could highlight awards or achievements specifically related to coding, technology, or problem-solving in software development.

This is a weak area. This project is a tutorial video, it has minimal impact for demonstrating expertise and might show the inexperience in web applications for business. Therefore, the project should be removed.
